Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.65,0:00:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 天亮啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.65,0:00:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,快起床啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 快起床
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.60,0:00:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,天亮啦 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.45,0:00:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是缪啊 早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.00,0:00:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就起来 别拍脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.85,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,始 缪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.40,0:02:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么爸爸和月姐姐总是光着身子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.35,0:02:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等缪再长大点就会懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,长大了就会懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 会懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.75,0:02:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸也是因为这里变大了所以才懂吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.95,0:02:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过缪没有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.65,0:02:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,缪不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 听我说 女孩子没有这个很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,再过十年 不对二十年 干脆一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,都千万不要碰这东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.60,0:03:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,早餐准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 早上大家为缪做了早餐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,有缪最喜欢的全鱼宴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.65,0:03:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,所以你们二位赶紧把衣服穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.95,0:03:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊 别教坏缪了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,从梅尔基涅海底遗迹回来已经六天了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.85,0:03:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,待得太久了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多该…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 今天玩什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.40,0:03:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.10,0:04:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.30,0:04:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,今天就随便做点新装备
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那缪也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.90,0:04:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.00,0:04:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那是当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好 今天做点什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好 接下来大家一起玩鬼捉人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.10,0:04:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们所有人都是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.55,0:04:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 跑快点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,得出发了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,该怎么跟缪说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她会哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.00,0:05:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定会哭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,和过去一刀两断什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.95,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,请不要选择如此寂寞的生存方式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我恨你 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,小心 缪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.70,0:05:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 缪去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.60,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.05,0:05:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 鬼捉人不是这种游戏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 快还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.06,0:05:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.85,0:05:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:05:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,突然这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我没做什么值得道谢的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟你为了女儿百般烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.60,0:06:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,作为母亲 自然想说一句谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,被看穿了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且我还是想瞒着你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.90,0:06:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 没人不知道的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.00,0:06:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}缪 不能偷东西呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,月她们也有所考虑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.85,0:06:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,缪真是遇上了一群非常好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.45,0:06:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,大家真的做得足够好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 请不要烦恼 朝该走的路前进吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.05,0:06:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,能够遇上各位 那孩子也成长了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,以前她可是只会撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,现在也懂得主动关心别人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.05,0:07:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子心里也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你们必须再次出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.30,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}缪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她年纪还小 可能动不动就喜欢撒娇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但她也从来没对你们说过不要走 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她也明白 不能再继续挽留你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,沦落到让一个小孩子操心也太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.10,0:07:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 今晚我会好好说清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,明天我们就出发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那今晚就大餐一顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,也作为你们的饯别会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.90,0:07:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我很期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 敬请期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,老 公
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.40,0:08:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 这个称呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.10,0:08:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅 有胆量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅小姐 什么时候
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真是不能掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,从不同的角度来看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,就像在侍奉主人一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,露出play 玩得真开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.10,0:08:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,多谢款待
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 缪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐的泳衣该还回来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,月
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.20,0:08:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,香织
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,缪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,送给爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说缪 是始大人叫你来偷我的泳衣的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人真是的 说一声不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,始 我的也给你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我也一样 如果始想要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,上面和下面想要哪件？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.95,0:09:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说两件都要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.00,0:09:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,蕾蜜雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.15,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不能再见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,缪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸走了之后 还能一直当缪的爸爸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,如果缪想要的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那就路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,而且 下次就轮到缪去迎接爸爸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.90,0:09:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,迎接？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:10:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 我要去非常遥远的地方 所以
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 既然爸爸能去的话缪也能去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,缪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为缪可是爸爸的女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.00,0:10:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,等处理完所有事情 一定会回到缪的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,和大家一起来见缪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.30,0:10:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.45,0:10:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 我有骗过你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,回来之后 就带上缪一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然后带你们一起去看看我出生的故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸出生的地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.55,0:10:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定能让你大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.85,0:10:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我的故乡就跟吓人箱一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我想看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.45,0:10:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,期待吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,特别期待
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.95,0:11:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那就听话和妈妈一起等着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不要做危险的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好好听妈妈的话 努力帮妈妈干活
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.30,0:11:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.40,0:11:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸 妈妈也一起去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这个嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,当然 不会把我排除在外吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.50,0:11:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,话是这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但那里真的和这个世界大不相同
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.05,0:11:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,女儿和老公要去的地方我怎么可能不去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 缪 来帮忙一起准备晚餐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.05,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你要带她们去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.45,0:11:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不同意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.70,0:11:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这是始做的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:11:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.55,0:12:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然有点出乎意料
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.00,0:12:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 本来以为现在的始应该会直接道别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,遇上缪之后主人也稍微变了一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.90,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 要是找不准时机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.35,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,就算找到了回去的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,也不一定随时随地都能用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.15,0:12:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那就想尽办法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,不论如何我也会回到缪身边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,也要让她看看日本
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.50,0:12:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,如果要我抛下缪穿越世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就想尽一切办法再次回到这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.60,0:12:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不论穿越多少次都行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.95,0:12:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不就是这么简单吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 就这么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.25,0:12:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,来这里之后的第一次放置play
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,饭做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,好 来大吃一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.40,0:13:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,护身符？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,是附身符
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:20.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.05,0:13:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 缪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.65,0:13:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我会好好珍藏的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.35,0:13:26.60,Default,,0,0,0,,妾身也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大家和缪的都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 缪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们出发了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.40,0:13:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐们也是 一路顺风
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.55,0:14:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们出发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,缪 我们一定会再回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前你就乖乖等着我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.40,0:14:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.85,0:14:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那究竟是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:15:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不仅如此 父王的样子也有点奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这里已经没有能信任的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.40,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 终于万事俱备了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.20,0:15:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人兴奋不已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我魂牵梦绕的那一瞬间 终于要到来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.75,0:15:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你们把我关起来 想对学生们做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,等等 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.50,0:15:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,一切遵从主之意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.90,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,已经退下棋盘的你 不必知会这些
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.05,0:15:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,南云
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,尽管来吧 异种
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.45,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,那时就是你的终结之时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.80,0:16:11.45,Default,,0,0,0,,神谕降临了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.50,0:16:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,神的代言人 我们的魔王陛下发令了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,毁灭异教徒！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,昭示神之旨意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,彰显吾之强大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.90,0:16:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,让妄自支配北大陆的愚昧之人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.60,0:16:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,认清自己的实力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.07,Screen,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(980,690)\bord2\c&H181616&\3c&HFFFFFF&}海利希王国-忠灵塔-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.50,0:16:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,王宫里不断扩散的现象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:17:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,让骑士和士兵们无力化的失神 究竟是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.85,0:17:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,团长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题吧 何塞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 没被任何人看见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,兵团的情况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,包括兵团长在内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,队长级别的大部分人都有失神的症状
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,海利希总战力的三成啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是某些人发起的攻击吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,单纯就是累了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不要乐观主义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.90,0:17:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,何塞 小心你也会中招的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.55,0:17:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.10,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 团长这边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.55,0:17:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下有受到什么影响吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.50,0:17:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,陛下目前还没有失神的征兆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.90,0:17:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,不如说更加霸气了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.90,0:17:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,说着以主之名 绝不饶恕魔人族的蛮行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.70,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,团长？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.05,0:17:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,何塞 召集精通暗属性魔法的人过来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:02.15,Default,,0,0,0,,找出失神的真相 让他们制定对策
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.65,0:18:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,明白 光辉他们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.90,0:18:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我来应对
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们现在正处于不安定的时期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不想给他们增添压力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.50,0:18:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,仅削弱士气的魔法吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,考虑魔人族所为比较合理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.10,0:18:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,直接攻击王宫？不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.05,0:18:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就算能做到 为什么不用更强力的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,既然能使用魔法而不被察觉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.85,0:18:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么不对我动手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.50,0:18:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,只要取下骑士团长性命
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,士气必将一蹶不振
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:19:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙 如今在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.65,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我有什么不测
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.90,0:19:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,希望一定要送达
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,送给安卡吉公国的杰根主公
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,以及南云始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 梅尔德团长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 桧山
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大介？这么晚了有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 有件事情我必须找梅尔德团长商量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.40,0:19:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 多有打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.20,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我不太想让班上的那些人听见
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.05,0:19:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.45,0:19:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 没什么打扰的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.00,0:19:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你先说说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,心里怎么想就怎么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么问题 应该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.85,0:20:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我来一起帮你想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.20,0:20:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,团长 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.15,0:20:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,何塞？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.60,0:20:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,事情紧急必须立即报告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,梅尔德团长 没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我在走廊等你们说完
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 不好意思啊 大介
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.10,0:20:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.75,0:20:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,何塞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.70,0:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 果然是洗脑了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,原谅我可能会伤到你 何塞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.85,0:21:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这股力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.05,0:21:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大介 你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.90,0:21:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,接我这招 副团长
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,呼啸 遍野之风
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大介
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.90,0:23:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 危险的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:59.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.87,0:01:05.71,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:11.05,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.34,0:01:17.47,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.97,0:01:22.89,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.60,0:01:26.65,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:28.48,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.73,0:01:34.41,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:40.37,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.37,0:01:46.08,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:51.51,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.97,0:01:54.76,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.34,0:02:00.10,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.73,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.23,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.95,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.84,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.39,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.48,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.07,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.12,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.58,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:21.17,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:26.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.18,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:12.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆为虚空一场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.73,0:22:17.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破灭的希望　虚伪的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.15,0:22:23.95,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身体的伤口深不见底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.24,0:22:29.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不仅是我　你也背负同样的伤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.58,0:22:38.29,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得谁人原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:42.84,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕怀中相拥　徒留轮廓难辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.84,0:22:47.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘愿承伤不曾犹豫的代价
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.64,0:22:52.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹒跚　忍痛离开你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.52,0:22:57.48,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:02.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.07,0:23:07.07,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}几步对错　令我身负百孔千疮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.12,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形单影只渐行渐远
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.41,0:23:16.58,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　谁人不曾拥有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.83,0:23:21.17,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.17,0:23:26.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凛然在上　抛下两难抉择
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:31.18,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不断拷问你我
